 Nigerian Stock Exchange  Transactions in the shares of United Bank for Africa (UBA) topped the activity chart with 24.407 million shares valued at N171.573 million.  
  
Access Bank followed with 19.132 million shares worth N148.117 million, while Mutual Benefits Assurance traded 17.877 million shares valued at N6.852 million.
  
